{"tid":1169294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"染6病毒手提電腦當藝術品　網上拍賣叫價逾900萬","createTime":"2019-05-24T09:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T10:55:03.000Z","uid":75969,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9b0207fbe73eea931407264b1dd94b45f986820c","tid":1169294,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190524/s00005/1add7155be3cf94def56e14f04e52169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190524%2Fs00005%2F1add7155be3cf94def56e14f04e52169.jpg&h=b7fbf940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一部感染6種強力電腦病毒的手提電腦，被當作藝術品在網上拍賣，截至本港時間今午（24日）5時，叫價已高達1,200,749美元（逾942萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n拍賣這部已屆11歲「高齡」的中毒三星（Samsung）手提電腦，是藝術家Guo O Dong與美國紐約網絡保安公司Deep Instinct合作、名為「The Persistence of Chaos, 2019」的計劃。在美國，為造成破壞而出售惡意軟件屬違法，故拍賣條款已列明，這部中毒手提電腦的買家必須「視之為藝術品，或為學術理由買入電腦」。電腦已被隔離於網絡外。<br />\n<br />\n但網絡保安專家難以理解拍賣計劃目的，專家Kevin Beaumont向英國廣播公司（BBC）表示，只要把沒有安裝任何防毒軟件或安全漏洞修補程式（security patches）的手提電腦連上互聯網數天，就可得到一部同樣感染這麼多病毒的電腦，還可「省下（用作競拍的）百萬美元」。<br />\n<br />\n被拍賣手提電腦感染的病毒包括：<br />\n<br />\nWannaCry：於2017年攻擊全球多國電腦的病毒，本港亦有商業機構和家庭用戶受影響<br />\n<br />\nILoveYou：2000年出現的電腦病毒，在兩周內感染5000萬部電腦，美國中情局與國防部和英國國會亦受影響<br />\n<br />\nMyDoom：於2004年出現、曾被指是「史上傳播速度最快」的電腦病毒，透過電郵傳播<br />\n<br />\nSoBig：2003年出現的電腦病毒，BBC引述一間網絡保安公司表示，高峰期時每17封電郵就有一封內含這病毒<br />\n<br />\nDarkTequila：用作竊取財務資料與電腦帳戶登入資料的鍵盤記錄惡意程式<br />\n<br />\nBlackEnergy：2016年被用作攻擊烏克蘭電網的電腦病毒<br />\n<br />\n（BBC）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190524/s00005/1558688779330/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190524%2Fs00005%2F1558688779330%2F&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=501f40f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190524%2Fs00005%2F1558688779330%2F&h=e698e515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190524/s00005/1558688779330/</a><br />\n<br />\n養蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78765db297623f32796ea888bf9c0efe4cede3a2","tid":1169294,"uid":51720,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"用強國電腦，都係藝術品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69771b2dfd25f5e99a153c688614cb676aec2f1f","tid":1169294,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"華為電話裝多個監控軟件的話又可唔可以當藝術品賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd8bfee606e8698d4ea48e8f267558e8d940edd","tid":1169294,"uid":9526,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾機, HAO123都無"},{"pid":"908d5a7b3feefefdb72b8a4fa253fee84890d1cd","tid":1169294,"uid":33868,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"連hao123、金山毒霸都無"},{"pid":"91b8aa342dd9afea0945f9f74371fb2de013bb65","tid":1169294,"uid":249885,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"hao123 支山毒霸 一齊down 可以當部機係鬥獸場"},{"pid":"237779d6c1327357c18f012c1d432287cd34fe44","tid":1169294,"uid":104833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fd8bfee606e8698d4ea48e8f267558e8d940edd","tid":1169294,"uid":9526,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾機, HAO123都無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ea9180f788ae901179af311744a09d57b760e8","tid":1169294,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"91b8aa342dd9afea0945f9f74371fb2de013bb65","tid":1169294,"uid":249885,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1